hands_on_practices.solution:
不动点 $\mathbf{x}^*$ 满足
$$
(I - A)\mathbf{x}^* = \mathbf{b}\,.
$$
此处
$$
I - A = \begin{pmatrix}
1-a & -c & 0 \\
-c & 1-a & 0 \\
0 & 0 & 1-d
\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{3}{4} & -\frac{1}{8} & 0 \\
-\frac{1}{8} & \frac{3}{4} & 0 \\
0 & 0 & \frac{2}{3}
\end{pmatrix}.
$$

该 $2\times2$ 子矩阵的行列式为
$$
\det = \Bigl(\tfrac{3}{4}\Bigr)^2 - \Bigl(-\tfrac{1}{8}\Bigr)^2
=\frac{9}{16}-\frac{1}{64}
=\frac{35}{64}\,,
$$
因此其逆矩阵为
$$
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{3}{4} & -\frac{1}{8} \\
-\frac{1}{8} & \frac{3}{4}
\end{pmatrix}^{-1}
=\frac{64}{35}
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{3}{4} & \frac{1}{8} \\
\frac{1}{8} & \frac{3}{4}
\end{pmatrix}.
$$

因此，对于 $\mathbf{b}_{12}=(\tfrac14,\tfrac14)^T$ 我们得到
$$
\begin{pmatrix}x^*\\y^*\end{pmatrix}
=\frac{64}{35}
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{3}{4}&\frac{1}{8} \\
\frac{1}{8}&\frac{3}{4}
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}\tfrac14\\ \tfrac14\end{pmatrix}
=\frac{64}{35}\begin{pmatrix}\frac{7}{32}\\ \frac{7}{32}\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}\frac{14}{35}\\ \frac{14}{35}\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}\frac{2}{5}\\ \frac{2}{5}\end{pmatrix}.
$$

对于 $z$ 分量，
$$
z^*=\frac{\;b_3\;}{1-d}
=\frac{\tfrac14}{\tfrac23}
=\frac{3}{8}.
$$

因此，总和为
$$
S = x^* + y^* + z^* = \frac{2}{5} + \frac{2}{5} + \frac{3}{8} = \frac{4}{5} + \frac{3}{8} = \frac{47}{40}.
$$
